snippet.title: Moonlight In Garland Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Moonlight in Garland is a cozy, life-sim that sees you making a new start in the bustling metropolis of Garland. 

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1441770/Moonlight_In_Garland/

Find an apartment and make it perfectly yours, befriend your neighbours, grow your garden, solve community problems and experience all the weirdly wonderful stuff that city living offers.

Find your feet, make a positive impact and live your best life in Garland!
